designed this for @maluma courtesy of @hennessyus way back in feb of this year 🥃💘 

behold this behemoth chain with camo set cuban links, the juiciest gemstones ive ever laid eyes on and his logo as a pendant with the crown serving as the bale. all colors were based on maluma's limited edition hennessy packaging. pleased to finally share this one with you🪩

🫶🏻💍 Got to work with @sean_wotherspoon and @netflix to make custom rings inspired by the love story in #YouPeople. Check out how we did it and meet Jesse and Alejandra, co-founders of @pasosforoakcliff 🫶🏻🫶🏻 i love these rings so much lol. we do this for fun !💘😶‍🌫️ 

-with love and gratitude, RG

PEMDAS (please excuse my dusty ass sketch book) 

Found the first sketch of the umlaut link amongst a poorly updated to-do list from back in sept. Here This Friday. 🫶🏻

This Friday we will release our new signature chain link - the UMLAUT link. Wearing this chain in 18kt is a divine experience all around. The 'puffiness' or width keeps movement between the links at bay , and *just* the right weight sits on your collarbones, wrist or ankle. It's just solid...and Light bounces off of these links differently than your usual cable link would too, thanks to the umlaut dots. It's intriguing from afar and up close...i could write love letters to this chain all day lol. This Friday🫶🏻
